     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     CJAKHZ
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    CJHIN1
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    CJHIN2
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    CJHIN3
